The country was founded by Sir Kim Hiram in 1624, who overthrew the Mfoewfwsk Government. They had a civil war in 1865, but quickly defeated the rebels. They fought with the Allies in an international war in the 1910s against the Axis, and also joined the Allies in the 1940s (unless this is a completely different timeline, WWI was between the Entente and Central Powers, not Allies and Axis). Another uprising took place in 1965, but was quelled in a massacre known as Black Saturday. In the 2010s, there was a war with Alcaida and EFCC, in which they were swiftly defeated. They also had economic depressions in 1935, 1968, and 2016.
